      </h2>
      
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <a href="/cuotas" 
           class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-400 text-slate-900 font-semibold py-4 px-10 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(245,158,11,0.3)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(245,158,11,0.5)] hover:-translate-y-1">
